<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="ida7d040dd-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s501"><num value="501">§ 501.</num><heading> Definition</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this chapter “enlistment” means original enlistment or reenlistment.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="ida7d040de-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/90/235/s2/a/1/B">Pub. L. 90–235, § 2(a)(1)(B)</ref>, <date date="1968-01-02">Jan. 2, 1968</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/81/753">81 Stat. 753</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
